{"word":"G4835 - συμπαθής - sympathḗs - soom-path-ace' - Having compassion one of another","slug":"G4835","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπαθής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>sympathḗs"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soom-path-ace'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Having compassion one of another"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03BC;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03B8;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C2; - sumpathe&#x0304;s</b> - <i>soom-path-ace'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>; <i>having a fellow feeling</i> (&ldquo;sympathetic&rdquo;), that is, (by implication) <i>mutually commiserative:</i> - having compassion one of another."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841\">G4841</a>"}]}